title: (Almost) Complete Mars Attack Collection [June 2014]
description:
Up to date collection of Mars Attacks comics as of June 28th 2014. Missing the following issues:


[Pocket Comics]

Mars Attacks 1-4


[Topps Comics]

Mars Attacks-Classic Card Series 004
Mars Attacks-Classic Card Series 005




In latin countries, the classic cards series comics were published under "Mars Attacks: Untold Tales". Ive found the spanish issues online 1-5 scanned, but not the last 2 issues in english. Im not sure if theyve been scanned yet, but if anyone has them, please upload and help complete this collection for everyone. 



As a bonus, I also uploaded all of the card scans I could find. If anyone has complete collections of the 1994 re-release by Topps or the 2013 set, share it with us and round out the archive.





Have a hell of a Saturday guys!


                                                                     RIP Magazine3k
